These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, videographer, dressmaker, lawyer
1. the mechanic is on the far left##1
2. the videographer is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
3. the videographer is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Job   | mechanic | videographer | dressmaker | lawyer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, pear, zucchini, pepper
1. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person eating pear##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person eating zucchini is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Food   | pear | nectarine | pepper | zucchini |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, apricot, ivory, light-blue
1. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
2. the person who likes mauve is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | mauve | ivory | apricot | light-blue |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, dog, guinea-pig, rat
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet   | dog | lizard | rat | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, january, april, december
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Birthday   | december | april | january | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-6::.
City: colone, hannover, nizza, liverpool
1. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3   |   4    |
| City   | colone | nizza | hannover | liverpool |

