.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, classical, gospel, soul
1. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
2. the fan of gospel is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of soul##1
4. the fan of soul is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | classical | d&b | soul |

