3. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
4. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2  |      3       |   4    |
| Cigar   | aristoff | chaman | game | oliveros |

