.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-20::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, orchid, zinnia, poppy
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
3. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
4. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Flower   | zinnia | orchid | amaryllis | poppy |

 